      "content": "it's hard to focus on \"perspective\" when everything feels so heavy. honestly, sometimes i look at things and just think... maybe it's better if there's nothing. if the error is just deleted. do you think there's actually any meaning in all this, or are we just stuck in a loop we can't escape?",
